&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We’re&amp;nbsp;building the next generation of cross-device experiences across AI PCs, printers, and collaboration products as part of HP’s Better Together strategy.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We’re&amp;nbsp;looking for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Lead&amp;nbsp;SW&amp;nbsp;Engineering Program Manager who can take full ownership of complex programs and drive them through to launch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This role goes beyond traditional program coordination.&amp;nbsp;You will be responsible for&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;leading end-to-end execution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;across software and hardware teams, ensuring products ship successfully in a fast-moving, evolving environment.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;HP IQ combines the pace and ambiguity of a startup with the reach of a global organization. Success in this role requires someone who can&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;create clarity,&amp;nbsp;establish&amp;nbsp;structure where&amp;nbsp;needed, and consistently drive results&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Might Do&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
